data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom/ 2 bathroom ranch style home on a full unfinished basement!  This one has gorgeous hardwoods in the living areas, a split bedroom plan, a huge great room with fireplace, and a  large kitchen with stainless steel appliances.  The master suite is on the main level with an oversized bathroom including double vanities, a garden soaking tub and a separate shower.  Full unfinished basement is plumbed for a bathroom and has tons of storage as well!  Gorgeous deck overlooking the lush backyard with invisible fence.  On a corner lot in a beautiful neighborhood with sidewalks, a pool and tennis courts, this one has been well-loved and is ready for it's new owners to love on it as well!
